<p t="1051" d="4939" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Um, thank you so much,​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​Fukami-san.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="6657" d="2402" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I couldn&#39;t have found​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​my pencil case without you.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="9693" d="1335" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​No thanks needed.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="11028" d="2302" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​And just call me Shiina.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="13330" d="2703" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​I&#39;ll call you Shino, too.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="16033" d="4471" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Oh, all right.​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​In that case, Shiina-san.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="21338" d="3303" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Please do allow me to​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​express my thanks, though.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="25442" d="3137" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​This was given to me​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​by my grandmother.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="28979" d="2536" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Really? Good thing​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​we found it, then.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="31515" d="767" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Yes!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="32883" d="3337" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​So I am really,​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​truly grateful to you!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="36820" d="1769" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Sure. Oh yeah, Shino.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="39089" d="2002" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Just one more thing.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="41492" d="1635" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​What is it?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="43627" d="1735" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​You&#39;re better off keeping​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​your distance​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="45362" d="2536" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​from that kid​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​while you&#39;re at school.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="48699" d="1968" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​It&#39;s for your own good.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="51135" d="2802" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Hanging out with the popular kid​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="53937" d="1702" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​will only get you unnecessary​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​jealousy and spite.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="56440" d="3136" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Um, so you&#39;re saying,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="60911" d="5639" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I shouldn&#39;t become friends​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​with them?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="66550" d="1869" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="71155" d="2235" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I... I see...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="73991" d="1968" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Hey, if you ever need​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​someone to talk to,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="75959" d="2136" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​just come to me.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="78462" d="4037" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Shiina-san... Thank you.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
</body>
